items.text: User Course Detail — this dashboard shows a detailed snapshot of a user's activity in one of their enrolled courses. Use the tabs in the following sections to switch between views, such as category and subcategory breakdowns, as well as between different content types such as lessons, practice, and tests. To return to this user's other enrollments or to switch to a different user, use the navigation buttons above.
